36 630 Td
0.102 0.102 0.102 rg
("People would sign up, poke around for two days, and then ghost," Sarah Chen, Head of Growth at Bloom, told us. "We'd email them once or twice asking if they needed help, but it was too generic. We didn't know where they were getting stuck.") Tj
